abstract: Wilson Kipsang of Kenya wins the Frankfurt Marathon in 2 hours 3 minutes 42 seconds.
snippet: Wilson Kipsang of Kenya recorded the second-fastest official marathon time in winning the Frankfurt Marathon in 2 hours 3 minutes 42 seconds.
lead_paragraph: Wilson Kipsang of Kenya recorded the second-fastest official marathon time in winning the Frankfurt Marathon in 2 hours 3 minutes 42 seconds.
